text: Last.fm is a music website from the UK. It started in 2002. It provides Internet radio, and a community for music discussion. It has more than 19 million users.Jemima Kiss (February 28, 2008). Last.fm widgets boost user numbers. The Guardian. Accessed September 8, 2008. == References == == Other websites == * Last.fm homepage Category:British entertainment websites Category:Music websites
